TODO

=head1 ARGUMENTS

=over 8

=item * C<-h>

 Print help.

=item * C<--version>

 Print version of script.

=item * C<dwg_file>

 AutoCAD DWG file.

=back

=head1 EXAMPLE

 dwg-status -h

